description: This app will tell you what ingredients are in my favorite recipes. It won't tell you the actual recipe though. You need to make your own way!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask my recipes how do you make salsa
Alexa, ask my recipes what is the recipe for honey mustard chicken
ask my recipes, how do I make cranberry and cream cheese dip
name: My Recipes
shortDescription: Ask Alexa for the ingredients to my favorite recipes
